body:

Midoriya: Hey, it’s okay, you’re gonna make it

Midoriya: of course, anything

Kirishima, on the phone: yo wuddup

Kaminari: hey… I, uh… I’m in a bit of a situation… I need you to do something for me…

Kirishima: yeah, man, sure

Kaminari: delete… My browser history

Kirishima: oh, yeah, can do. You dying?

Kaminari: yeah, you know what to do

Kaminari and Kirishima hang up
